      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FULL NOISE (7) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a 1.5 lengths second (26.24) in a Grade 5 at this track. Meets a moderate line up and rates on top this time. JUMBUK WANG WANG (4) has been hard to follow lately, running eighth (27.14) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Rates a winning chance on best. MISS JAZZ (2) finds it hard to break through. Finished second (26.02) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Solid record here winning three races. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Bold showing expected. DESPICABLE ANDY (8) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
